Tarek Alarian (amụrụ na Septemba 12, 1963) bụ onye nduzi ihe nkiri Palestine-Ijipt
A na-akpọkwa ya Tarek El'eryan na Tarek Eryan.
Alarian nwere nzere Bachelor of Arts na Communication nakwa Cinema na Photography na Mahadum Southern Illinois.
